sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Web/Mobile App
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant BAL as Balance Service
    participant B as Bus (Event Bus)
    participant N as Notification Service

    U->>W: Record "I paid Sarah 300" (full or partial)
    W->>G: POST /settlements
    G->>BAL: Record settlement
    Note over BAL: Check amount <= owed<br/>No confirmation needed from other side
    BAL->>BAL: Update balance_pair + save settlement
    BAL-->>G: 201 Created
    G-->>W: Balance updated
    BAL->>B: Publish "settlement.recorded"
    B->>N: Deliver event
    N->>N: Notify the other person
